{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775852361878,"sessionID":"ses_286f3a7a4ffedCaqyidW5cR7P9","part":{"id":"prt_d790c94260016RBozzjTeq2ALO","messageID":"msg_d790c819f001nO0yFEDv7WvaIu","sessionID":"ses_286f3a7a4ffedCaqyidW5cR7P9","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"call_f5fbd8daf18047c997f1fa83","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-020/tasks.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-020/tasks.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AR-020 — CLI pack 命令 — Tasks\n2: \n3: > **Module:** cmd/cli\n4: > **Language:** Python\n5: > **Size:** M\n6: > **Precondition:** Stage ST-3 (Design) completed\n7: > **Reference:** `changes/AR-020/proposal.md`, `changes/AR-020/design.md`, `changes/AR-020/delta-spec.md`, `cli-toolkit/design.md`, `cli-toolkit/spec.md`\n8: \n9: ## T1. 创建 Python CLI 项目脚手架\n10: \n11: - [ ] 1.1 创建 `cmd/cli/` 目录\n12: - [ ] 1.2 创建 `cmd/cli/pyproject.toml`，包含：\n13:   - `name = \"agentcube\"`, `requires-python = \">=3.10\"`, `version = \"0.1.0\"`\n14:   - `[project] dependencies`: typer[all]>=0.9.0, pydantic>=2.0.0, pyyaml>=6.0, httpx>=0.24.0, docker>=6.0.0, rich>=13.0.0, packaging>=23.0, importlib-resources>=6.0.0, semver>=3.0.0\n15:   - `[project.optional-dependencies]`: k8s, dev, test（与 cli-toolkit/design.md 依赖表一致）\n16:   - `[project.scripts]`: `kubectl-agentcube = \"agentcube.cli.main:app\"`\n17:   - `[tool.setuptools] packages`: agentcube, agentcube.cli, agentcube.runtime, agentcube.operations, agentcube.services\n18:   - `[tool.pytest.ini_options]`: testpaths = [\"tests\"]\n19:   - `[tool.ruff]`, `[tool.mypy]` 基础配置\n20: - [ ] 1.3 创建包目录结构：\n21:   - `cmd/cli/agentcube/__init__.py`（`__version__ = \"0.1.0\"`, `__author__`, `__email__`, 导出占位）\n22:   - `cmd/cli/agentcube/cli/__init__.py`\n23:   - `cmd/cli/agentcube/models/__init__.py`\n24:   - `cmd/cli/agentcube/runtime/__init__.py`\n25:   - `cmd/cli/agentcube/services/__init__.py`\n26:   - `cmd/cli/agentcube/operations/__init__.py`\n27:   - `cmd/cli/tests/__init__.py`\n28: - [ ] 1.4 创建 `.gitignore`（`__pycache__/`, `*.pyc`, `.pytest_cache/`, `dist/`, `build/`, `*.egg-info/`）\n29: - [ ] 1.5 运行 `pip install -e cmd/cli[dev]` 确认安装成功\n30: - [ ] 1.6 运行 `ruff check cmd/cli/agentcube/` 和 `mypy cmd/cli/agentcube/` 确认工具链可用\n31: \n32: **Verification:** `pip install -e cmd/cli[dev]` exit 0；`python -c \"import agentcube; print(agentcube.__version__)\"` 输出 `0.1.0`；ruff 和 mypy 无致命错误\n33: \n34: ---\n35: \n36: ## T2. 实现 MetadataOptions 数据类 — agentcube/models/pack_models.py\n37: \n38: - [ ] 2.1 创建 `cmd/cli/agentcube/models/pack_models.py`\n39: - [ ] 2.2 定义 `MetadataOptions` dataclass，字段与 cli-toolkit/design.md §MetadataOptions 表一致：\n40:   `agent_name: Optional[str] = None`\n41:   `language: Optional[str] = \"python\"`\n42:   `entrypoint: Optional[str] = None`\n43:   `port: Optional[int] = 8080`\n44:   `build_mode: Optional[str] = \"local\"`\n45:   `requirements_file: Optional[str] = None`\n46:   `description: Optional[str] = None`\n47:   `workload_manager_url: Optional[str] = \"\"`\n48:   `router_url: Optional[str] = \"\"`\n49:   `readiness_probe_path: Optional[str] = \"\"`\n50:   `readiness_probe_port: Optional[int] = 8080`\n51:   `registry_url: Optional[str] = \"\"`\n52:   `registry_username: Optional[str] = \"\"`\n53:   `registry_password: Optional[str] = \"\"`\n54:   `agent_endpoint: Optional[str] = \"\"`\n55: - [ ] 2.3 实现 `@classmethod from_options(cls, options: Dict[str, Any]) -> \"MetadataOptions\"` 类方法：\n56:   - 从 options dict 中提取已知字段，忽略未知字段\n57:   - 返回 `MetadataOptions` 实例\n58: - [ ] 2.4 创建 `cmd/cli/tests/models/test_pack_models.py`\n59: - [ ] 2.5 测试 `TestMetadataOptions_Defaults`：无参构造 → 所有字段为默认值\n60: - [ ] 2.6 测试 `TestMetadataOptions_FromOptions_Full`：完整 options dict → 字段完全匹配\n61: - [ ] 2.7 测试 `TestMetadataOptions_FromOptions_Partial`：部分 options dict → 缺失字段为默认值\n62: - [ ] 2.8 测试 `TestMetadataOptions_FromOptions_UnknownFields`：含未知字段 → 忽略未知字段，已知字段正确\n63: \n64: **Verification:** `pytest cmd/cli/tests/models/test_pack_models.py -v` 全部通过\n65: \n66: ---\n67: \n68: ## T3. 实现 AgentMetadata Pydantic 模型 — agentcube/services/metadata_service.py（部分）\n69: \n70: - [ ] 3.1 创建 `cmd/cli/agentcube/services/metadata_service.py`\n71: - [ ] 3.2 定义 `AgentMetadata(BaseModel)`，字段与 cli-toolkit/design.md §AgentMetadata 表一致：\n72:   `agent_name: str`（required）\n73:   `description: Optional[str] = None`\n74:   `language: str = \"python\"`\n75:   `entrypoint: str`（required）\n76:   `port: int = 8080`\n77:   `build_mode: str = \"local\"`\n78:   `region: Optional[str] = None`\n79:   `version: Optional[str] = None`\n80:   `image: Optional[Dict[str, Any]] = None`\n81:   `auth: Optional[Dict[str, Any]] = None`\n82:   `requirements_file: Optional[str] = \"requirements.txt\"`\n83:   `registry_url: Optional[str] = \"\"`\n84:   `registry_username: Optional[str] = \"\"`\n85:   `registry_password: Optional[str] = \"\"`\n86:   `agent_endpoint: Optional[str] = None`\n87:   `workload_manager_url: Optional[str] = None`\n88:   `router_url: Optional[str] = None`\n89:   `readiness_probe_path: Optional[str] = None`\n90:   `readiness_probe_port: Optional[int] = None`\n91:   `agent_id: Optional[str] = None`\n92:   `session_id: Optional[str] = None`\n93:   `k8s_deployment: Optional[Dict[str, Any]] = None`\n94: - [ ] 3.3 实现 Pydantic v2 validators（`@field_validator`）：\n95:   - `validate_language`: 限制为 `['python', 'java']`，转小写\n96:   - `validate_build_mode`: 限制为 `['local', 'cloud']`，转小写\n97:   - `validate_port`: 范围 1–65535\n98: - [ ] 3.4 创建 `cmd/cli/tests/services/test_metadata_model.py`\n99: - [ ] 3.5 测试 `TestAgentMetadata_ValidCreation`：合法字段 → 模型创建成功\n100: - [ ] 3.6 测试 `TestAgentMetadata_ValidateLanguage_Python`：`language=\"Python\"` → 规范化为 `\"python\"`\n101: - [ ] 3.7 测试 `TestAgentMetadata_ValidateLanguage_Java`：`language=\"java\"` → 通过\n102: - [ ] 3.8 测试 `TestAgentMetadata_ValidateLanguage_Rejected`：`language=\"nodejs\"` → `ValidationError`\n103: - [ ] 3.9 测试 `TestAgentMetadata_ValidateBuildMode_Local`：`build_mode=\"local\"` → 通过\n104: - [ ] 3.10 测试 `TestAgentMetadata_ValidateBuildMode_Cloud`：`build_mode=\"cloud\"` → 通过\n105: - [ ] 3.11 测试 `TestAgentMetadata_ValidateBuildMode_Rejected`：`build_mode=\"hybrid\"` → `ValidationError`\n106: - [ ] 3.12 测试 `TestAgentMetadata_ValidatePort_Valid`：`port=8080` → 通过\n107: - [ ] 3.13 测试 `TestAgentMetadata_ValidatePort_Zero`：`port=0` → `ValidationError`\n108: - [ ] 3.14 测试 `TestAgentMetadata_ValidatePort_Overflow`：`port=70000` → `ValidationError`\n109: - [ ] 3.15 测试 `TestAgentMetadata_ModelDump`：`model_dump(exclude_none=True)` 不包含 None 字段\n110: \n111: **Verification:** `pytest cmd/cli/tests/services/test_metadata_model.py -v` 全部通过；覆盖 delta-spec §Port validation 和 §Build mode validation 和 §Language validation 全部场景\n112: \n113: ---\n114: \n115: ## T4. 实现 MetadataService — YAML 加载/保存与回退链\n116: \n117: - [ ] 4.1 在 `metadata_service.py` 中定义 `MetadataService` 类：\n118:   - `__init__(self, verbose: bool = False)`\n119: - [ ] 4.2 实现 `load_metadata(self, workspace_path: Path) -> AgentMetadata`：\n120:   - 按回退链尝试加载：`agent_metadata.yaml` → `agent.yaml` → `metadata.yaml`\n121:   - 使用 `yaml.safe_load()` 解析 YAML\n122:   - 将 dict 传入 `AgentMetadata(**data)` 构造模型\n123:   - 三个文件都不存在时返回 `None`\n124: - [ ] 4.3 实现 `save_metadata(self, workspace_path: Path, metadata: AgentMetadata) -> None`：\n125:   - 使用 `yaml.dump(metadata.model_dump(exclude_none=True), default_flow_style=False, indent=2, sort_keys=False)`\n126:   - 写入 `{workspace_path}/agent_metadata.yaml`\n127: - [ ] 4.4 实现 `update_metadata(self, workspace_path: Path, updates: Dict[str, Any]) -> AgentMetadata`：\n128:   - 先调用 `load_metadata` 加载现有元数据\n129:   - 如不存在则创建默认 `AgentMetadata`\n130:   - 合并 updates dict 到现有模型（使用 `model_copy(update=updates)` 或等价方式）\n131:   - 调用 `save_metadata` 保存\n132:   - 返回更新后的 `AgentMetadata`\n133: - [ ] 4.5 创建 `cmd/cli/tests/services/test_metadata_service.py`\n134: - [ ] 4.6 测试 `TestLoadMetadata_PrimaryExists`：`agent_metadata.yaml` 存在 → 正确加载\n135: - [ ] 4.7 测试 `TestLoadMetadata_FirstFallback`：仅 `agent.yaml` 存在 → 正确加载\n136: - [ ] 4.8 测试 `TestLoadMetadata_SecondFallback`：仅 `metadata.yaml` 存在 → 正确加载\n137: - [ ] 4.9 测试 `TestLoadMetadata_NoneExist`：三个文件都不存在 → 返回 `None`\n138: - [ ] 4.10 测试 `TestSaveMetadata_RoundTrip`：保存后重新加载 → 数据一致\n139: - [ ] 4.11 测试 `TestSaveMetadata_ExcludeNone`：保存的 YAML 不包含 null 值\n140: - [ ] 4.12 测试 `TestSaveMetadata_Format`：YAML 使用 `default_flow_style=False, indent=2, sort_keys=False`\n141: - [ ] 4.13 测试 `TestUpdateMetadata_Merge`：部分更新 → 未更新字段保留原值\n142: - [ ] 4.14 测试 `TestUpdateMetadata_CreateNew`：无现有文件 → 创建新元数据\n143: \n144: **Verification:** `pytest cmd/cli/tests/services/test_metadata_service.py -v` 全部通过；覆盖 delta-spec §Metadata loading with fallback chain 全部 4 个场景\n145: \n146: ---\n147: \n148: ## T5. 实现工作区验证 — PackRuntime._validate_workspace_structure\n149: \n150: - [ ] 5.1 创建 `cmd/cli/agentcube/runtime/pack_runtime.py`\n151: - [ ] 5.2 定义 `PackRuntime` 类：`__init__(self, verbose: bool = False)`，存储 `self.verbose` 和 `self.metadata_service = MetadataService(verbose=verbose)`\n152: - [ ] 5.3 实现 `_validate_workspace_structure(self, workspace_path: Path) -> None`：\n153:   - 路径不存在 → `ValueError(f\"Workspace path does not exist: {workspace_path}\")`\n154:   - 路径不是目录 → `ValueError(f\"Workspace path is not a directory: {workspace_path}\")`\n155: - [ ] 5.4 创建 `cmd/cli/tests/runtime/test_pack_runtime_workspace.py`\n156: - [ ] 5.5 测试 `TestValidateWorkspace_ValidDirectory`：有效目录 → 无异常\n157: - [ ] 5.6 测试 `TestValidateWorkspace_NotExists`：路径不存在 → `ValueError`\n158: - [ ] 5.7 测试 `TestValidateWorkspace_IsFile`：路径是文件而非目录 → `ValueError`\n159: - [ ] 5.8 测试 `TestValidateWorkspace_SymlinkToDirectory`：符号链接指向目录 → 通过\n160: \n161: **Verification:** `pytest cmd/cli/tests/runtime/test_pack_runtime_workspace.py -v` 全部通过；覆盖 delta-spec §Workspace validation — not a directory 场景\n162: \n163: ---\n164: \n165: ## T6. 实现元数据加载与创建 — PackRuntime._load_or_