9:   - 根据 `metadata.language` 分发到 `_validate_python_compatibility` 或 `_validate_java_compatibility`\n230: - [ ] 9.2 实现 `_validate_python_compatibility(self, workspace_path: Path) -> None`：\n231:   - 检查至少一个 `*.py` 文件存在 → 无则 `ValueError(\"No Python files found in workspace\")`\n232:   - 如 `requirements_file` 指定，检查该文件存在 → 无则 `ValueError(f\"Dependency file not found: {requirements_file}\")`\n233: - [ ] 9.3 实现 `_validate_java_compatibility(self, workspace_path: Path) -> None`：\n234:   - 检查 `pom.xml` 存在 → 无则 `ValueError(\"pom.xml is required for Java projects\")`\n235:   - 验证 `pom.xml` 为有效 XML（`xml.etree.ElementTree.parse`）→ 无效则 `ValueError(\"Invalid pom.xml: not valid XML\")`\n236: - [ ] 9.4 创建 `cmd/cli/tests/runtime/test_pack_runtime_validation.py`\n237: - [ ] 9.5 测试 `TestValidateLanguageCompatibility_Python`：Python 语言 → 调用 `_validate_python_compatibility`\n238: - [ ] 9.6 测试 `TestValidateLanguageCompatibility_Java`：Java 语言 → 调用 `_validate_java_compatibility`\n239: - [ ] 9.7 测试 `TestValidatePython_HasPyFiles`：有 `.py` 文件 → 通过\n240: - [ ] 9.8 测试 `TestValidatePython_NoPyFiles`：无 `.py` 文件 → `ValueError`\n241: - [ ] 9.9 测试 `TestValidatePython_MissingRequirements`：指定 requirements_file 不存在 → `ValueError`\n242: - [ ] 9.10 测试 `TestValidatePython_CustomRequirements`：自定义 requirements_file 存在 → 通过\n243: - [ ] 9.11 测试 `TestValidateJava_HasPomXml`：有效 `pom.xml` → 通过\n244: - [ ] 9.12 测试 `TestValidateJava_NoPomXml`：无 `pom.xml` → `ValueError`\n245: - [ ] 9.13 测试 `TestValidateJava_InvalidPomXml`：`pom.xml` 非有效 XML → `ValueError`\n246: \n247: **Verification:** `pytest cmd/cli/tests/runtime/test_pack_runtime_validation.py -v` 全部通过；覆盖 delta-spec §Python compatibility validation 和 §Java compatibility validation 和 §Workspace validation — Java-specific 全部场景\n248: \n249: ---\n250: \n251: ## T10. 实现依赖处理 — PackRuntime._process_dependencies\n252: \n253: - [ ] 10.1 实现 `_process_dependencies(self, workspace_path: Path, metadata: AgentMetadata) -> None`：\n254:   - 根据 `metadata.language` 分发到 `_process_python_dependencies` 或 `_process_java_dependencies`\n255: - [ ] 10.2 实现 `_process_python_dependencies(self, workspace_path: Path) -> None`：\n256:   - 读取 `requirements_file`（默认 `requirements.txt`）\n257:   - 验证文件格式（非空行应为有效 pip 依赖格式）\n258:   - 文件不存在时静默跳过（已在 T9 验证阶段检查）\n259: - [ ] 10.3 实现 `_process_java_dependencies(self, workspace_path: Path) -> None`：\n260:   - 解析 `pom.xml` 提取依赖信息（仅作验证，不修改）\n261:   - 验证 `pom.xml` 包含 `<dependencies>` 节点（可选，仅记录 warning）\n262: - [ ] 10.4 创建 `cmd/cli/tests/runtime/test_pack_runtime_dependencies.py`\n263: - [ ] 10.5 测试 `TestProcessDependencies_Python`：Python 语言 → 调用 `_process_python_dependencies`\n264: - [ ] 10.6 测试 `TestProcessDependencies_Java`：Java 语言 → 调用 `_process_java_dependencies`\n265: - [ ] 10.7 测试 `TestProcessPythonDependencies_ValidRequirements`：有效 `requirements.txt` → 通过\n266: - [ ] 10.8 测试 `TestProcessPythonDependencies_CustomFile`：自定义 requirements_file → 读取正确文件\n267: - [ ] 10.9 测试 `TestProcessJavaDependencies_ValidPom`：有效 `pom.xml` → 通过\n268: - [ ] 10.10 测试 `TestProcessJavaDependencies_NoDependencies`：`pom.xml` 无 `<dependencies>` → 通过（仅 warning）\n269: \n270: **Verification:** `pytest cmd/cli/tests/runtime/test_pack_runtime_dependencies.py -v` 全部通过；覆盖 delta-spec §Dependency processing 全部场景\n271: \n272: ---\n273: \n274: ## T11. 实现 Python Dockerfile 生成 — PackRuntime._generate_python_dockerfile\n275: \n276: - [ ] 11.1 实现 `_generate_python_dockerfile(self, metadata: AgentMetadata) -> str`：\n277:   - 生成 Dockerfile 内容，包含：\n278:     - `FROM python:3.10-slim`\n279:     - `WORKDIR /app`\n280:     - `COPY {requirements_file} .`（或 `requirements.txt`）\n281:     - `RUN pip install --no-cache-dir -r {requirements_file}`\n282:     - `COPY . .`\n283:     - `EXPOSE {metadata.port}`\n284:     - `CMD [\"{entrypoint_parts...}\"]`（entrypoint 按空格分割为 JSON array）\n285:   - 返回 Dockerfile 内容字符串\n286: - [ ] 11.2 创建 `cmd/cli/tests/runtime/test_pack_runtime_dockerfile_python.py`\n287: - [ ] 11.3 测试 `TestGeneratePythonDockerfile_BaseImage`：包含 `FROM python:3.