{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775852379244,"sessionID":"ses_286f3a7a4ffedCaqyidW5cR7P9","part":{"id":"prt_d790cd9c3001orbdLvWAI9kVda","messageID":"msg_d790cccc7001FqxdC5zpflIYHm","sessionID":"ses_286f3a7a4ffedCaqyidW5cR7P9","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"call_0df67d07fcbc417bb37f5e7d","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-021/design.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-021/design.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AR-021 — CLI build 命令 — Design\n2: \n3: ## 1. Architecture\n4: \n5: ### 1.1 Purpose\n6: \n7: <!-- TODO: Describe the purpose and role of the CLI build command -->\n8: \n9: ### 1.2 Package Layout\n10: \n11: <!-- TODO: Describe the directory and package structure -->\n12: \n13: ### 1.3 Data Flow\n14: \n15: <!-- TODO: Describe the data flow and component interactions -->\n16: \n17: ### 1.4 Dependencies\n18: \n19: <!-- TODO: List direct dependencies and their purposes -->\n20: \n21: ---\n22: \n23: ## 2. Data Structures\n24: \n25: <!-- TODO: Define data structures, types, and constants -->\n26: \n27: ---\n28: \n29: ## 3. API Contracts\n30: \n31: <!-- TODO: Define CLI command interface, arguments, flags, and output formats -->\n32: \n33: ---\n34: \n35: ## 4. Core Implementation\n36: \n37: <!-- TODO: Describe the core implementation approach -->\n38: \n39: ---\n40: \n41: ## 5. Error Handling\n42: \n43: <!-- TODO: Define error categories, handling strategies, and sentinel errors -->\n44: \n45: ---\n46: \n47: ## 6. Testing Strategy\n48: \n49: <!-- TODO: Define unit test matrix, integration tests, and gate requirements -->\n50: \n51: ---\n52: \n53: ## 7. Deployment Considerations\n54: \n55: <!-- TODO: Describe deployment, packaging, and operational considerations -->\n56: \n57: ---\n58: \n59: ## 8. Implementation Steps\n60: \n61: <!-- TODO: Break down